So many times I've bought music thinking it would sound just like when I first heard it. And when you listen to the music, it's just a bit off and IMHO, not better than the original. But this buy of Haunted Heart IS the original and brought back so many wonderful memories. Another BIG plus was making this purchase on Amazon because I can listen to this on my Kindle, Office or Home Laptop and my Ipod.
